  .subForumsPopup a .dt, .subForumsPopup a .arrowWidget:before, .subForumsPopup a.PopupControl .dt, .subForumsPopup.Popup .PopupControl.PopupOpen, .moderatorToolsPopup a .dt, .moderatorToolsPopup a .arrowWidget:before {
